Class PVector

  • java.lang.Object
    • PVector
  • public class PVector
extends Object
    Vector class is useful for doing physics, physical simulations and simple games. This class focuses on 2D vectors only. All angles are computed in degrees Vector math included is: Vectors as components (x, y) or standard vector (magnitude, angle) Vector addition and subtraction Scalar only operations: multiplication, division Finding the unit vector: unit() or normalize() Static methods: angleBetween, magnitudeDiff
